rComments: Super passionate about his field and the lives of his students, all around seems like a great guy and prof. Highly recommend.

He is passionate about what he teaches! He loves rock climbing, and so far, I've learned quite a lot from it. In my opinion, he talks REALLY fast, and it was hard taking notes for his class. Thankfully, it was online so I had the recordings, but it took me a couple of hours to watch because I had to keep pausing. Other than that, he is pretty good!
He talks about nothing but climbing. I wish he would climb me. XoX
